      "code": "class Solution {\npublic:\n    double findMaxAverage(vector<int>& nums, int k) {\n        int n = static_cast<int>(nums.size());\n        long long windowSum = 0;\n\n        for (int i = 0; i < k; ++i) {\n            windowSum += nums[i];\n        }\n\n        long long bestSum = windowSum;\n        for (int right = k; right < n; ++right) {\n            // Keep exactly k numbers: add the new right end and remove\n            // the number that just moved out from the left end.\n            windowSum += nums[right];\n            windowSum -= nums[right - k];\n            bestSum = max(bestSum, windowSum);\n        }\n\n        // Cast before division so C++ keeps the fractional part.\n        return static_cast<double>(bestSum) / k;\n    }\n};"
