      "code": "class Solution {\npublic:\n    int superEggDrop(int k, int n) {\n        vector<long long> covered(k + 1, 0);\n        int moves = 0;\n\n        while (covered[k] < n) {\n            ++moves;\n\n            for (int eggs = k; eggs >= 1; --eggs) {\n                // The break branch loses one egg; the safe branch keeps eggs.\n                covered[eggs] = covered[eggs] + covered[eggs - 1] + 1;\n            }\n        }\n\n        return moves;\n    }\n};"
