      "code": "class Solution {\npublic:\n    int pivotIndex(vector<int>& nums) {\n        int rightSum = accumulate(nums.begin(), nums.end(), emptySideSum);\n        int leftSum = emptySideSum;\n\n        for (int index = firstIndex; index < static_cast<int>(nums.size());\n             ++index) {\n            rightSum -= nums[index];\n\n            // After removing nums[index], rightSum contains only elements\n            // strictly to the right of the current index.\n            if (leftSum == rightSum) {\n                return index;\n            }\n\n            leftSum += nums[index];\n        }\n\n        return noPivotIndex;\n    }\n\nprivate:\n    static constexpr int firstIndex = 0;\n    static constexpr int emptySideSum = 0;\n    static constexpr int noPivotIndex = -1;\n};"
