      "code": "class Solution {\npublic:\n    int pivotIndex(vector<int>& nums) {\n        int n = static_cast<int>(nums.size());\n        vector<int> prefixSum(n + prefixPadding, emptyPrefixSum);\n\n        for (int index = firstIndex; index < n; ++index) {\n            prefixSum[index + currentElementOffset] =\n                prefixSum[index] + nums[index];\n        }\n\n        int totalSum = prefixSum[n];\n        for (int index = firstIndex; index < n; ++index) {\n            int leftSum = prefixSum[index];\n            int rightSum =\n                totalSum - prefixSum[index + currentElementOffset];\n\n            // prefixSum[index] ends before index, and prefixSum[index + 1]\n            // ends after index, so the current value is excluded from both.\n            if (leftSum == rightSum) {\n                return index;\n            }\n        }\n\n        return noPivotIndex;\n    }\n\nprivate:\n    static constexpr int firstIndex = 0;\n    static constexpr int prefixPadding = 1;\n    static constexpr int currentElementOffset = 1;\n    static constexpr int emptyPrefixSum = 0;\n    static constexpr int noPivotIndex = -1;\n};"
