      "sourceUrl": "https://leetcode.cn/problems/powx-n/description/",
      "code": "class Solution {\npublic:\n    double myPow(double x, int n) {\n        long long exp = n;\n        if (exp < zeroExponent) {\n            x = oneValue / x;\n            exp = -exp;\n        }\n        return positivePower(x, exp);\n    }\n\nprivate:\n    static constexpr long long zeroExponent = 0;\n    static constexpr long long evenRemainder = 0;\n    static constexpr long long splitFactor = 2;\n    static constexpr double oneValue = 1.0;\n\n    double positivePower(double base, long long exp) {\n        if (exp == zeroExponent) {\n            return oneValue;\n        }\n\n        double half = positivePower(base, exp / splitFactor);\n        double squared = half * half;\n        if (exp % splitFactor == evenRemainder) {\n            return squared;\n        }\n        return squared * base;\n    }\n};"
