      "sourceUrl": "https://leetcode.cn/problems/product-of-array-except-self/description/",
      "code": "class Solution {\npublic:\n    vector<int> productExceptSelf(vector<int>& nums) {\n        int n = nums.size();\n        vector<int> prefix(n, 1);\n        vector<int> suffix(n, 1);\n\n        for (int i = 1; i < n; ++i) {\n            prefix[i] = prefix[i - 1] * nums[i - 1];\n        }\n        for (int i = n - 2; i >= 0; --i) {\n            suffix[i] = suffix[i + 1] * nums[i + 1];\n        }\n\n        vector<int> answer(n);\n        for (int i = 0; i < n; ++i) {\n            answer[i] = prefix[i] * suffix[i];\n        }\n\n        return answer;\n    }\n};"
