      "sourceUrl": "https://leetcode.cn/problems/coin-change/description/",
      "code": "class Solution {\npublic:\n    int coinChange(vector<int>& coins, int amount) {\n        const int impossible = amount + 1;\n        vector<int> dp(amount + 1, impossible);\n        dp[0] = 0;\n\n        for (int sum = 1; sum <= amount; ++sum) {\n            for (int coin : coins) {\n                if (coin > sum) {\n                    continue;\n                }\n                dp[sum] = min(dp[sum], dp[sum - coin] + 1);\n            }\n        }\n\n        if (dp[amount] == impossible) {\n            return -1;\n        }\n        return dp[amount];\n    }\n};"
